profiles.about: Musician turned software developer, creator of BandBlend.

Crowmouth is a Nu Metalcore act from Birmingham, Alabama. They combine fast-paced grooves, dissonant leads, and crushing breakdowns to create a sound that is both heavy and melodic. Their lyrical content is often dark and personal, exploring themes of sorrow, anguish, and self-loathing.
We are an energetic and dynamic band, bringing the best of rock and pop music to the world.

Hey there, I'm Lily, a singer-songwriter based in the heart of Columbus, Ohio. Music has been my lifeline since I was a child, and my soul finds solace in weaving heartfelt lyrics and melodies. With each song, I aim to share my journey and connect with listeners on a profound level, inviting them to join me on this emotional musical adventure.

Hello there, I'm Ella Johnson, a passionate violinist based in the vibrant city of New York, NY. From a young age, the violin has been my closest companion, and its enchanting melodies have shaped my life's journey. Music is my soul's language, and through the strings of my violin, I strive to evoke emotions that touch the hearts of audiences. From classical symphonies to contemporary collaborations, I embrace a diverse repertoire that reflects the rich cultural tapestry of New York. I love collaborating with other musicians and bands, so if you're in need of a violinist, please get in touch!

Introducing The Night Riders, a powerhouse rock band hailing from the heart of Chicago. With a relentless spirit and an electrifying stage presence, we've been tearing up the city's music scene with our high-octane performances and anthemic sound. Our music is a fusion of raw energy, blistering guitar riffs, and soul-stirring vocals, inviting listeners into a world of passion and rebellion. Drawing inspiration from the gritty streets and vibrant culture of Chicago, we infuse our music with an unmistakable urban edge. So buckle up and join us on this wild ride as we rock the night away and leave our mark on the city that fuels our rock 'n' roll dreams.

Hey, I'm Lucas Parker, a skilled guitarist and composer residing in the vibrant city of Los Angeles, CA. Through my instrumental music, I craft mesmerizing soundscapes that transport listeners to otherworldly realms. Drawing inspiration from life's intricacies, my guitar melodies narrate stories without words, inviting audiences to embark on a captivating sonic journey.

Hey, we're Electric Pulse, a synth-driven band proudly hailing from the vibrant city of Seattle, WA. Our music is an electrifying journey that delves into retro-futuristic landscapes, blending the essence of the past with a modern twist. For us, it's all about playing what we love, creating music that resonates with our souls, and sharing our passion with our incredible fans. We're not all about constant touring; we embrace a casual approach, letting the music speak for itself and connecting with our audience on an authentic level. We're always looking for new musicians to collaborate with and feature, so hit us up if you're interested!

Hi there, I'm Olivia Turner, a talented country-pop singer-songwriter proudly hailing from the heart of Nashville, TN. Music is my passion, and through heartfelt songs, I strive to capture the beauty of life and love, weaving emotions into every lyric and melody. Join me on this musical journey as we embrace the soulful essence of country and the infectious charm of pop, creating harmonies that resonate with the hearts of listeners far and wide. Together, let's paint a canvas of emotions through the power of music.

We are Sunset Groove, a vibrant band hailing from the sunny city of Miami, FL. With our catchy melodies and infectious rhythms, we live to create music that gets you moving and grooving. Drawing inspiration from the rich cultural tapestry of Miami, our sound is a fusion of diverse influences that come together in a harmonious celebration of life and music.

Hey, Max here. I'm a guitarist from the beautiful town of Orlando. Through my music, I aim to capture moments of love, longing, and self-discovery, taking listeners on an emotional journey they won't forget.

I am Aurora Beats, an electronic music producer and DJ based in the vibrant city of San Francisco, CA. My beats are crafted to create an ethereal atmosphere on the dance floor, transporting listeners to a world of mesmerizing sounds and infectious rhythms.
Sophie Martinez is a talented jazz vocalist and pianist from Los Angeles, CA. Her music evokes the classic sounds of the golden era.

We are Rising Tide, a rock band hailing from the heart of Austin, TX. Our music is an infusion of anthemic songs and raw energy that ignites the stage during our electrifying live performances. With each chord, we aim to leave an indelible mark on the hearts of our audience, riding the waves of music that define the essence of Rising Tide.

I'm Leo Thompson, a passionate singer-songwriter hailing from the breathtaking city of Denver, CO. With my soulful voice and introspective lyrics, I aim to enchant audiences and connect with their hearts through the power of music.

Hey there, we are Galactic Fusion, a dynamic hip hop duo hailing from the vibrant city of San Diego, CA. Our music is a celestial concoction of otherworldly sounds and infectious grooves, pushing the boundaries of hip hop and taking our listeners on a cosmic journey through the depths of space and time. Drawing inspiration from the wonders of the universe, our beats transport you to distant galaxies, where the rhythm of the cosmos meets the energy of the streets. With each track we craft, we aim to break free from the confines of the ordinary, creating a fusion that resonates with the souls of those who dare to explore the uncharted realms of hip hop. So buckle up and join us on this interstellar voyage, as we blend genres and minds, and let the power of music transcend the limits of our imagination. Together, let's make music that leaves an indelible mark on the universe. 🌌

Hey there, I'm Mia Roberts, a passionate indie-pop singer-songwriter hailing from the enchanting city of Portland, OR. My music is an ethereal blend of dreamy melodies and introspective lyrics that aim to captivate hearts and transport listeners to a world of emotions. Through my songs, I strive to explore the complexities of life and connect with souls in the most profound ways.

We're Velvet Skies, a metal band from Miami, FL. We formed in 2019 and have quickly become one of the most exciting new bands in the scene. Our music is a mix of heavy breakdowns, soaring vocals, and catchy melodies. We've toured all over the US and have opened for some of the biggest names in metal. Velvet Skies is on the rise and we're sure to be one of the biggest bands in metal in the years to come.

I'm Noah Adams, a bass player from Austin, TX. I've been playing music since I was a kid, and I'm passionate about creating music that is both beautiful and meaningful. My music is inspired by the beauty of nature and human connections. I love the way music can bring people together and create a sense of community. I'm always looking for new opportunities to collaborate with other musicians, and I'm eager to join a band that shares my vision for music.

Alright, listen up, folks! I'm Johnny Silverfinger, the one and only! I've seen it all during my wild years on the road as a steeldrum player, stuff you can't even imagine. Now though, I pretty much run the show here at BandBlend...and I'm stuck answering your dumb questions. Sure, my senses might not be what they used to be, but you'll have to deal with it cause it's what you're getting. Since I'm getting paid for it, come talk to me if you need help with the site or want to hear about some of the crazy $&@! from when I was on the road. Just make it quick, I ain't got all day.

Seeking a talented drummer to complete our band's rhythm section. Our musical journey has been a fusion of passion and creativity, and we need someone who can groove with us on stage and in the studio. If you've got the beats, and you're hungry for musical exploration, hit us up for a jam session. We believe that when diverse minds and talents converge, extraordinary things happen. Let's create something magical together!
Just dropped my latest single on all major platforms! Give it a listen and let me know what you think. Your feedback means the world to me!

Just dropped our latest single on all major platforms! This song has been a labor of love, and we're thrilled to share it with all of you. From the heartfelt lyrics to the infectious melody, it encapsulates the essence of our musical journey. We hope it becomes the soundtrack to your life's moments, whether joyful or reflective. Give it a listen and let us know what you think. Your support means the world to us, and together, we can spread the power of music far and wide.
Calling all guitarists! My normal guitarist won't be able to play on my upcoming run of shows. Hit me up if you're interested in the spot!
Had a great time performing at a local open mic night last night! 🎤 Met some amazing fellow musicians and got to share our music with the audience. Looking forward to the next gig!
Working on some new song ideas in the studio today. Can't wait to share them with you all!
Just released a new single! 🎉 Check it out on Spotify and let us know what you think!

Calling all guitarists! Our band is embarking on a sonic adventure, traversing through genres and pushing musical boundaries. We need a lead guitarist with soulful expressions and electrifying solos to join our crew. We're not just looking for a musician; we're searching for a musical storyteller who can speak volumes through their instrument. If you're ready to embark on this journey, reach out to us.
Excited to announce that I'll joining a band I met on here to to play at a local music festival next month! Can't wait to share the stage with them in front of a larger audience!
Taking a break from gigs and spending some quality time in the studio, recording a few covers. Stay tuned for the release! 🎧
Just finished collaborating with an amazing singer on a new track. Can't wait for you all to hear it!

The band took a little trip to a live jazz performance last night. Not really our cup of tea normally, but WOW. We all left feeling so inspired. We want to incorporate some of that sound in our new tracks. Anybody proficient in jazz out there? Hit us up, we'd love to jam!
Had an amazing time playing a surprise acoustic set at a local cafe this morning. Music really brightens up everyone's day! 🎤
Spent the weekend at a songwriting workshop. Feeling refreshed and full of new ideas! Can't wait to put them into songs.
Just released a music video for our latest single! Check it out on YouTube and let us know what you think!
Hitting the road for a mini-tour next week. Excited to visit new cities and meet music lovers from all around.

Just wrapped up recording my new solo album, and I couldn't be more thrilled to share it with all of you soon! 🎶🎤 This album is a labor of love, pouring my heart and soul into each track. Stay tuned for updates and release dates – can't wait to take you all on this musical journey with me!

Drummer wanted! 🥁 I'm on the lookout for a skilled percussionist to join me on this musical voyage. If you've got the rhythm and the passion to bring my acoustic melodies to life, let's connect and create something beautiful together. Drop a message, and let the music lead the way!
Rehearsing for an upcoming gig. These pre-show jitters are always exciting! 🎸🎵
Just met with some fellow musicians to plan a collaborative music project. Can't wait to see it come to life!
Feeling grateful for all the support from my fans! You all keep me going. 🙏🎵

Hey there, jazz enthusiasts! 🎶 Mark your calendars for an unforgettable evening of live music! 🌟 Join me and my band at [Venue Name] on [Date] as we transport you to the golden era of jazz. Get ready to swing and groove to the timeless melodies that will make your heart dance. Can't wait to see you there!

We're on the hunt for a new voice to join the Rising Tide! If you've got the passion and the power to rock the stage with our anthemic songs, we want to hear from you. Let's create magic together and take our music to new heights. Drop us a message or tag someone you think would be a perfect fit!
Performing at a local charity event tonight. So glad to be able to use music to make a positive impact.
Spent the afternoon in the recording booth laying down vocals. Can't wait for you all to hear these songs!🎙️

I can't wait to share the music I've poured my heart and soul into for my upcoming album. 🎤🎵 The songs are a reflection of life's ups and downs, and I hope they resonate with each one of you. Stay tuned for the release date and let's get ready to take this musical voyage together. Your support means the world to me!

Story time with Johnny! Let me take you on a wild ride down memory lane. Back in '89, we were tearing up the road, and this one time, we found ourselves in a quirky little town. The crowd was nuts, and so was I! I accidentally grabbed a tambourine instead of my steeldrum and ended up playing the craziest version of 'Sweet Child O' Mine.' Man, you should've seen the looks on their faces! Man, I miss those days. Good times, good times. Now I'm stuck here with all of you.

Tonight we will be dropping our next EP, Low Life. Our vocalist, Alec Harrah, wrote the majority of this EP from scratch. Not only is he able to pour his emotion into the music, but he is also an amazing song writer. Not many musicians can write the guitar, bass, drums, vocals, and synths for a song, much less a whole EP! But Alec can. He deserves all the credit for this one. It is an honor to play guitar for Crowmouth. I am excited to see how far we can go. Thank you to everybody who has come out to support us from social media to live shows. Everything we have right now is because of all of you! Thank you so much from the bottom of our hearts!
We will be performing a Crowmouth version of a Korn cover this Saturday night at Zydeco in Birmingham, AL! It will be our next released song as well...

Last night was hands down our favorite show. Thank you, Birmingham, for such an incredible evening. All of the bands that played absolutely destroyed their sets. It was an honor to share the evening with you all. We cannot wait to have more future shows with you guys. 🤘🖤

Last night's show was absolutely electric! 🎶🎤 Sharing the stage with the incredible drummer I found on BandBlend was a game-changer. The energy was through the roof, and the connection we had on stage was undeniable. Grateful for the power of music and the amazing collaborations it brings. Can't wait for the next gig!

🎧 Open to collaborations! 🎧 Whether you're a singer, songwriter, producer, or a fellow musician looking to add some country-pop flair to your tracks, I'm all ears! Let's join forces and infuse our unique styles to create something extraordinary. Shoot me a DM, and let's make music that speaks to the hearts of listeners worldwide!

🎶 Last night's gig was pure magic! 🌅 The crowd was on fire, and we couldn't have asked for a better response to our music. Big shoutout to our amazing fans for bringing the energy and dancing with us all night long. Special thanks to our fellow musicians who jammed with us on stage – you made it an unforgettable show! 🎉🎤

Seeking a talented rapper to feature on my upcoming track! If you've got the flow and the lyrical prowess to match the vibe of my beats, let's collaborate and create something truly magical. Drop me a message, and let's bring the perfect blend of electronic and rap to the music scene!

Attention all rhythm maestros! 🥁 I'm in search of a passionate percussionist to join my musical adventure. If you're a lover of jazz and know how to set the perfect groove, let's jam together and create some mesmerizing melodies. Whether you're a skilled drummer or play other percussive instruments, I'm eager to explore the magic we can create. Drop me a message, and let's bring the beat to life!

🎸 What a night! 🎸 Last night, we unleashed an instrumental set that shook the stage and left the crowd wanting more. 🌊🎶 The energy was electric, and we felt the connection with our fans in every note we played. Thank you to everyone who came out to support us! Stay tuned for more upcoming gigs and be prepared for even bigger waves of music coming your way!

I'm on the lookout for talented souls to form a band that's ready to hit the road and share our music with the world. If you're as eager as I am to create unforgettable melodies and connect with audiences from coast to coast, let's join forces and embark on a musical journey of a lifetime. Drop me a message, and let's start this adventure together! 🚌

We're on the hunt for a soulful voice to feature on our new track. If you've got the passion to infuse your vocals into our galactic beats, let's create something out of this world together. Drop us a message or tag someone who would be a perfect fit. Let's make music that transcends the boundaries of time and space!

Tour preparations in full swing! 🚀 We're getting ready to embark on a cosmic journey, bringing our infectious grooves to cities near you. 🎵🎉 Can't wait to meet all our incredible fans and share the energy of our live performances. Stay tuned for tour dates and let's make this intergalactic ride a memorable one!

Our beats are calling for some cosmic percussion to elevate our live shows and studio recordings. If you've got the groove and the passion for hip hop, let's connect and create music that moves the galaxies. Drop us a message, and let's make rhythmic magic together! 🌠🎵

I'm thrilled to announce that I'm looking to form a full band to bring my indie-pop vision to life. If you're a skilled instrumentalist or a soulful backing vocalist ready to embark on this musical journey with me, let's connect and create magic together. Drop me a message, and let's make music that resonates with the heart and soul. 🌟

What an unforgettable night! 🎉 I played a cool show a few nights ago that left me buzzing with excitement. The energy was electric, and the crowd's response to my music was absolutely heartwarming. Thank you all for being part of this musical journey. Your support means the world to me, and I can't wait to share more magical moments with you soon!

Why I write the music I write 📝 For me, music is an exploration of the human experience - the highs, the lows, and everything in between. My songs are like windows into my soul, where I pour my emotions, dreams, and fears into each lyric and melody. It's a way for me to connect with others and make sense of the world around me. I hope my music touches your heart and serves as a reminder that we're never alone in this journey called life.
Our new track 'The Breakdown' is out now! This is our heaviest song yet, so get ready to lose your head!
We're looking for a new bass player to join us on the road! If you're a killer bassist and you're down to tour the world, hit us up! We'd love to have you on the team.
Last night's show was insane! The mosh pit was so crazy, I thought the venue was going to collapse! Thanks to everyone who came out and gave us so much energy!

I'm looking for a band to join! I'm a bass player with a passion for creating music that is both beautiful and meaningful. I'm inspired by the beauty of nature and human connections. If you're looking for a bassist who is dedicated, hardworking, and creative, hit me up!
Had a great jam session with someone I met on BandlBlend last night! We played for hours and had so much fun. It's always great to find other musicians who are passionate about music as much as I am
"I just released my new track, 'The Heart of the Forest.' This song is about the power of nature to heal and connect us. I hope you enjoy it!
